twitter.content: RFK 🦾🇺🇸

posts.raw_content:
He was a good man and a voice for good in the world. His last words were related to us on his podcast via his recent cohost (ex wife?). 

I listened to Scott pretty much every day for about 8 years. We didn't always agree, but he had a good way of carefully sitting back and observing instead of letting the illusions produced by his mind rule him. His ability to carefully consider ideas and reframe them to understand other angles was valuable and a good example for anyone trying to be considerate of the world. He was a friend to Trump and surely influenced him in ways we could never know.

I will miss you Scott,

-H0rse

posts.raw_content:
He was a good man and a voice for good in the world. His last words were related to us on his podcast via his recent cohost (ex wife?). 

I listened to Scott pretty much every day for about 8 years. We didn't always agree, but he had a good way of carefully sitting back and observing instead of letting the illusions produced by his mind rule him. His ability to carefully consider ideas and reframe them to understand other angles was valuable and a good example for anyone trying to be considerate of the world. He was a friend to Trump and surely influenced him in ways we could never know.

I will miss you Scott,

-H0rse
